# Environment template

Copy to `.env` and fill before running `forge script`:

```
PRIVATE_KEY=0x...
ARB_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia-rollup.arbitrum.io/rpc
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=...
CHAINLINK_AGGREGATOR=0x...
TIMELOCK_MIN_DELAY_SECONDS=172800
GOV_INITIAL_SUPPLY=10000000000000000000000000
GOV_PROPOSAL_THRESHOLD=100000000000000000000000
ORACLE_HEARTBEAT_SECONDS=3600
TREASURY_FEE_BPS=500
ANNUAL_PREMIUM_BPS=800
```

Frontend (`apps/web/.env`):

```
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=...
VITE_COLLATERAL_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_VAULT_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_POLICY_MANAGER_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_CLAIM_PROCESSOR_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_GOVERNOR_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_GOV_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_GRAPHQL_ENDPOINT=https://api.studio.thegraph.com/query/.../shieldfi/...
```
